node.text: Much love to everyone reaching out with care and concern. Turns out I have hydronephrosis. In my case it’s something they say I was born with but just hadn’t had any problems until now. I’m doing great and will be fine. A little bump in the road but thankfully it’s fixable. I hope to only have to postpone a few weeks from the original date of May 8 to fight. Excited to get back in there and put it all on the line for you guys!!!

node.text: Just whipping up my favorite mix for a protein shake. Tasty and quick. No added crap in the protein and mixing in some powdered greens. You won’t be disappointed! Grab some of my protein from Amazon if you don’t have any already. I’ll post a swipe up link in my stories so you can easily grab some. And kick some ass this Friday 👊

node.text: I hope you all had such a special day celebrating Christmas with loved ones. I’ve been reflecting on my life and it’s many blessings. This Christmas is a special Christmas to me. I thank God for this day and every day I am alive. I am so thankful for Jesus our Lord who was sent here for us. He was sent to save us and give us hope. I just truly hope all of you are feeling blessed as well. Sending all my love and well wishes to you and your loved ones. Merry Merry Christmas !!!!! I probably said I’m sending all my love multiple times..... but well..... I just mean it. 😉

So here you have it!!

node.text: You know I’ll be tuning in to watch the fights tonight. The beauty of a fight… anything can happen in there. It’s what makes it fun to watch. The future is unknown and every second counts. You can dominate a fight and it can still slip through your fingers in the last remaining minutes. I’d love to get the chance to redeem that loss. You want to see it too? Holm vs Tate 2?
